Dangbana Republik artiste, Ahmed Abiola Akinbiyi Lawal, popularly known as Bella Shmurda or fine boi Bella has revealed he has an unforgiving nature. The “Vision 2020” singer disclosed this via his snap chat while sounding a note of warning to persons who would dare to offend him, whether knowingly or not.   Oxford University congratulates DJ Cuppy on thesis…     Estranged wife, Anita drags Paul Okoye to court over alleged…     I feel like getting married – Iyabo Ojo   According to him, no matter how long it takes, he’d always seek revenge against his offenders because he doesn’t believe in forgiveness. “I don’t believe in forgiveness. Before you offend me, think twice. “It might take tons of years, I will always strike back at the right time”, he said.